# -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

_REDUCE_LINE_POINTING_ - Reduce a heterodyne line pointing
observation.

=head1 DESCRIPTION

=head1 ARGUMENTS

=over 4

=back

=head1 NOTES

=over 4

=back

=head1 OUTPUT DATA

=over 4

=back

=head1 TASKS

=head1 REQUIRED PERL MODULES

=head1 AUTHORS

Brad Cavanagh E<lt>b.cavanagh@jach.hawaii.eduE<gt>

=head1 COPYRIGHT

